"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"之前一直在捣鼓本地部署ETH节点，太费事了，而且不容易维护，今天正好通过YouTube上学web3相关知识点，包含web3js,web3py…\\n\\n里面介绍了，Infura：\\n\\n[Ethereum API | IPFS API & Gateway | ETH Nodes as a Service | Infura](https://infura.io/dashboard)\\n\\n[Infura’s development suite provides instant, scalable API access to the Ethereum and IPFS networks. Connect your app to Ethereum and IPFS now, for free!](https://infura.io/dashboard)\\n\\n[infura.io](https://infura.io/dashboard)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/VGybOGGbMwB5P7raWh4OX.png?height=1384&width=2806)\\n\\n有了这个API，可以很轻松的跟ETH节点进行沟通，比如如何获取gas，区块等等，所有节点信息都可以获取，如果你想要跟合约进行交互也可以轻松实现。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/QTHoTja-qrPVItaJUAl8l.png?height=1410&width=2210)\\n\\n这是我测试的如何拉取OMG Network: OMG Token的简单交互，特别方便，强烈推荐👍🏻\",\"timestamp\":1641124585,\"title\":\"(1) 如何跟ETH节点交互\"},\"digest\":\"4p1yitZSb7K8NlJAinpceW5w8l5gRdTvRudCDjf6cMQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x3E00B9f8583849887F4Dfbd688fC27488325DCd3\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gOGN5uV84YX6vlnaz0iBV4_lGVpnI7ZVWph0T6pg8ms\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"k0qcGZZIN8rqcwATS6ABSkr49nIf9-bZ7rFtlutPT0Y\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"PzV9mUF-Hm3vqOBF5-RU_B9By7WQS5rlzN_ocg33bo2GTZBu1ELQaBUPakIDYoC-8B_SEAibqJMor4FlB6HyNA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xddde62a618ef35d070d3d9b24ba183631d828c299fc32e68c933bfddc851f51834d696923028218eb7e8479f932dc90d76288ea408ecc4832185da6bb791209e1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gOGN5uV84YX6vlnaz0iBV4_lGVpnI7ZVWph0T6pg8ms\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"k0qcGZZIN8rqcwATS6ABSkr49nIf9-bZ7rFtlutPT0Y\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"4p1yitZSb7K8NlJAinpceW5w8l5gRdTvRudCDjf6cMQ\"}"